snippet.title: Mortal Kombat: Komplete Edition - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready for more limb tearing action? The best fighting game is back with the Komplete Edition. Every downloadable character, every classic skin will be in. Not to be left out, the original theatrical movie and the soundtrack for the game has joined the party as well. Check out the trailer for some sweet bloody action!

Release Date: February 28, 2012
Platforms: Xbox 360, PS3
Genre: Fighting 
Publisher: Warner Bros. Interactive
Developer: NetherRealm Studios 
M for Mature

Fatality your way over to IGN for more:
http://xbox360.ign.com/objects/125/125777.html
